MongoDb is an open source database developed by MongoDb, Inc.
MongoDb stores data in JSON like structure.
It is a NoSql database.
MongoDb used BSON(Binary Javascript Object Notation) to query database.

# MysQL #                                            # MongoDb #
=>Table                                            =>Collection
=>Row                                              =>Document
=>Column                                           =>Field


Logical Operator
$and-all conditions must be true
condition 1               condition 2               result
T                              T                       T
T                              F                       F
F                              T                       F
F                              F                       F

$or-one conditions must be true
condition 1               condition 2               result
T                              T                       T
T                              F                       T
F                              T                       T
F                              F                       F

$not-all conditions must be true
condition 1                  result
T                              F                      
F                              T                   
                                                  
findById() is a built-in method from mongoose used to fetch a single document by its _id from MongoDB
findByIdAndUpdate() is a built-in method from mongoose used to find by its _id na dupdate it in one query.
findByIdAndDelete() is a built-in method from mongoose used to delete by its _id.


SELECT SPECIFIC FIELDS IN MONGOOSE, IN MONOGOOSE ,YOU CAN SELECT SPECIFIC FIELDS FROMA DOCUMENT USING THE .SELECT() METHOD THIS HELPS IN:
-IMPROVES PERFORMANCE
-REDUCE UNNCESSARY DATA
-HIDE SENSITIVE FIELDS(LIKE PASSWORD)